Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Joder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,¡J-Joder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Como sigas chupando de esa manera, eya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,¡E-Eyacularé en un p-periquete!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Esto es...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,¡Ay, madre!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,¡Y-Ya viene!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,¿Hoy también te apetece venir a mi casa?